Interface TranspositionTable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface TranspositionTable
    Common interface for transposition table containers.

    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)

    • Method Detail

      • get

        java.lang.Double get(GameState gameState,
                   double alpha,
                   double beta)
        Returns null or exact game value or suitable bound on it from the transposition table for given game state and alpha-beta window. Null is returned when the entry for given sate does not exist or when call conditions are not appropriate for a bound to be returned.
        Parameters:
        gameState - reference to game state
        alpha - alpha value
        beta - beta value
        Returns:
        exact game value or suitable bound
